    <section id="id22694911">
      <title>Activity: To find out about acid rain [LO 1.1, LO 1.2, LO 1.3, LO 3.2]</title>
      <para id="id22822035">ASSIGNMENT 10</para>
      <para id="id14164900">“Burning coal releases sulphur dioxide which causes rain to fall as acid rain. This disturbs the chemical balance of the soil and prevents plants from growing properly”.</para>
      <para id="id14222513">Do research on the formation of acid rain and the effect that it has on the environment. The following scientific process has to be followed for this investigative research project. Steps 1 – 7 must form part of the investigation. Step 7 involves preparing a report to be submitted to a policy-making body like the government, for instance.</para>
      <table id="id22296573" summary="">
        <tgroup cols="4">
          <colspec colnum="1" colname="c1"/>
