      <para id="id22755244">GUIDELINES FOR ASSESSMENT:</para>
      <para id="id22755248">The learner's progress towards gaining an acceptable level of performance has to be measured. The following table provides guidelines for assessing the different tasks set for assessment and indicates the performance levels.</para>
      <table id="id11490125" summary="">
        <tgroup cols="5">
          <colspec colnum="1" colname="c1"/>
          <colspec colnum="2" colname="c2"/>
